data.description:
Nestled in the heart of Richfield, this 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom brick home is an opportunity waiting!

This property boasts an unbeatable location, offering the ultimate in convenience. With easy access to Hwy 77, commuting becomes a breeze, connecting you effortlessly to all the attractions and opportunities that the Twin Cities have to offer.

The classic brick exterior not only lends character to the home but also serves as a sturdy foundation for your renovation aspirations. 

For those who love the outdoors, nearby parks offer a convenient escape. Located near shopping and restaurants. 

Home is being sold as-is. Water will not be turned on for inspections/appraisals. Home is not move in ready. If property was built prior to 1978, Lead Based Paint Potentially Exists.
